== Board of governors ==
Each year the membership of the National Academy of Television Arts & Sciences Northwest Chapter elects professionals to represent the Northwest community. While best known for The EMMYÂ® Awards and Silver Circle, which recognize outstanding achievements in the industry, NATAS Northwest represents an array of other exciting events available to our membership.
The Board of Governors is a working board which work together collaboratively to ensures the best interests of the membership.<ref name="urlBoard of Governors">{{cite web |url=http://www.natasnw.org/View-users-list/Board-of-Governors.html |title=Board of Governors |author=[[NATAS]] |authorlink= |coauthors= |date= |format= |work= |publisher= |pages= |language= |archiveurl= |archivedate= |quote= |accessdate=2010-07-15}}Board of Governors</ref>
